'''烟酸盐酸盐'''是一种化合物，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub>ClNO<sub>2</sub>，它由质子化的烟酸阳离子（C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub>NO<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>）和[[氯化物|氯离子]]构成，分子间存在O－H…Cl、N－H…O和N－H…Cl[[氢键|氢键]]。<ref name="Slouf2000">{{cite journal|last1=Slouf|first1=Miroslav|title=3-Carboxypyridinium chloride|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section E Structure Reports Online|volume=57|issue=1|year=2000|pages=o61–o62|issn=1600-5368|doi=10.1107/S1600536800019632}}</ref>它可由烟酸的甲醇溶液和盐酸的甲醇溶液反应得到。<ref name="Slouf2000" />它可以在铂的催化下于50 °C加压氢化，得到3-哌啶甲酸盐酸盐。<ref>Karpov, A. A.; Krasnikov, S. V.; Betnev, A. F.; Krasovskaya, G. G.; Chal'tsev, A. V. Catalytic hydrogenation of 2-​furan- and 2- and 3-​pyridinecarboxylic acids. ''Izvestiya Vysshikh Uchebnykh Zavedenii, Khimiya i Khimicheskaya Tekhnologiya'', 2007. 4: 44-46. ISSN: 0579-2991.</ref>

